creator: pindle_
descriptionHtml:
Pin Your Moment!

Pindle is a social photography platform that allows you to Pin and share photos around the world via the use of geotagging.

PIN
Pin photos of places you visit! Your real-time location will be automatically added via the use of geotagging! There is no more need to try typing an address in foreign languages while travelling as the location will automatically be filled in for you.
- Add your Pin to a specific category for easy reference!
- Every Pin has customizable privacy settings!
- Highlight your favorite memories to share with friends and family via the 'Best Place' feature.
- Show your support for local Startups and NGOs by adding a badge to your post!

DISCOVER
- Follow friends and explore different locations around the world!
- Follow must-try places recommended by our top Cartographers and Content-creators.
- Save your favorite Pins and photos using the “Bookmark” feature!

MAP
- See where your friends are hanging out, if they’ve shared their location with you.
- Share your Location Pins with your followers or privately, just for yourself!
- Discover real-time Pins from the community nearby, or across the world!


MEMORIES
- Look back on Pins you’ve saved with free cloud storage.
- Edit and send old moments to friends, or just simply save them to your gallery.

CHAT
- The feature is still in development. Please be patient as we are adding it as soon as possible!

COMMUNITY
- Share your experiences and write guides to contribute to our Pindle community.
- Share your photos with #PINDLE for a chance to be curated as a Pindle Cartographer! We can’t wait to see what you create!
- Every single one of our users are special and we would love to hear your feedback on how we can make this app better!

Pindle is a social photography platform that allows you to Pin and share photos around the world via the use of geotagging.

PIN
Pin photos of places you visit! Your real-time location will be automatically added via the use of geotagging! There is no more need to try typing an address in foreign languages while travelling as the location will automatically be filled in for you.
- Add your Pin to a specific category for easy reference!
- Every Pin has customizable privacy settings!
- Highlight your favorite memories to share with friends and family via the 'Best Place' feature.
- Show your support for local Startups and NGOs by adding a badge to your post!

DISCOVER
- Follow friends and explore different locations around the world!
- Follow must-try places recommended by our top Cartographers and Content-creators.
- Save your favorite Pins and photos using the “Bookmark” feature!

MAP
- See where your friends are hanging out, if they’ve shared their location with you.
- Share your Location Pins with your followers or privately, just for yourself!
- Discover real-time Pins from the community nearby, or across the world!


MEMORIES
- Look back on Pins you’ve saved with free cloud storage.
- Edit and send old moments to friends, or just simply save them to your gallery.

CHAT
- The feature is still in development. Please be patient as we are adding it as soon as possible!

COMMUNITY
- Share your experiences and write guides to contribute to our Pindle community.
- Share your photos with PINDLE for a chance to be curated as a Pindle Cartographer! We can’t wait to see what you create!
- Every single one of our users are special and we would love to hear your feedback on how we can make this app better!

descriptionShort: Pin Your Moment - social photography platform
title: Pindle

creator: pindle_
descriptionHtml:
If you love traveling and taking photos, this app is for YOU!

Share your photos with the world and be rewarded with gifts and prizes! 🎀✈️

Make new friends and connect with global communities! 🧙🦸

Organize your photos using our map-based cloud storage absolutely free! 📲📸

Give back to the community by donating to other users and NGOs! 🙌💌

Map your Life! 📸🗺️

Pindle is a map-based social media platform that allows you to create and share photos around the world via the use of geotagging.

🗺️ MAP
- Post photos of places you visit! Your real-time location will be automatically added via the use of geotagging! No more need to type an address in foreign languages while travelling as the location will automatically be filled in for you
- Share your photos with your followers or privately, just for yourself
- Add your photos to a specific category for easy reference
- Highlight your favorite memories to share with friends and family via the 'My Favorites' feature
- Add an NGO badge to your post to show your support and raise awareness about global issues

🔍DISCOVER
- Follow friends and explore different locations around the world
- Check out hidden gems shared by our ambassadors
- Save your favorite locations and photos using the “Pin” function
- Discover real-time pins from global users
- Filter your search using time and category themes

🧠 MEMORIES
- Travel back in time and revisit photos on the map
- Share your past travel moments with friends easily
- Keep your memories safe using free cloud storage


🎁👥 COMMUNITY & REWARDS
- Earn free Pindle Gems and exchange them for fantastic gifts and rewards!
- Like, comment or even send Gems to other users whom you like!
- Help support NGOs around the world by donating Gems

Every single Pindle user is special to us and we love to hear your feedback on how we can make this app better for you!
